  • Classes in com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.user used by com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.user 
    Class and Description
    UserGetCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to get the details of a User.
    UserGetCommand.Builder
    Builder used to build the desired command.
    UserListCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to get a list of searched Users.
    UserListCommand.Builder
    Builder used to build the desired command.
    UserRecord
    List record representing a User, from the list returned in the UserListResponse.
  • Classes in com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.user used by com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.internal.command.user 
    Class and Description
    UserGetCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to get the details of a User.
    UserGetResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a UserGetCommand, describing the details of the retrieved User.
    UserListCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to get a list of searched Users.
    UserListResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a UserListCommand, returning the list of retrieved UserRecords.
